    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>The foam globes round come riding fast<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="the_foam_globes_round_come_riding_fast_poem_glosses_contextual.php#FOAMGLOBES"/></l>
                    <l>Like snow upon the eddies cast</l>
                    <l>Forth from his cold &#x0026; silent tomb</l>
                    <l>Forth flies the river from the gloom<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="the_foam_globes_round_come_riding_fast_poem_glosses_contextual.php#RIVERFROMTHEGLOOM"/></l>
                    <l>The bars that echoed to his roaring</l>
                    <l>Those icy bars have burst before him</l>
                    <l>And now his chafed surges see</l>
                    <l>Bound high in laughing liberty</l>
                    <l>Oh frigidly the glacier pale</l>
                    <l>Bears broadly to the nether vale</l>
                    <pb facs="MSVIII78r"/>
                    <fw type="pageNum" place="top-right"><handShift new="#HANDWGC" medium="pencil"/>78</fw>
                    <l><handShift new="#HANDJR1833-34" script="cursive" medium="ink"/>Right in his cliffy shivered side</l>
                    <l>Yawneth a chasm high &#x0026; wide</l>
                    <l>And from the portal arched &#x0026; strong</l>
                    <l><del rend="strikethrough"><unclear resp="#DCH">Leap</unclear></del> Springs gladsome forth the <geogName corresp="#ARVERON">Arveron</geogName></l>
                    <l>Seems it an ancient forteresse<ref type="gloss_textual" target="the_foam_globes_round_come_riding_fast_poem_glosses_textual.php#FORTERESSE" /></l><!--The textual glosses in this work do not anchor/highlight corresponding foot note correctly.-->
                    <l>All shattered in its mightiness</l>
                    <l>The higher towers all rent &#x0026; riven</l>
                    <l>The battlements all downward driven<ref type="gloss_textual" target="the_foam_globes_round_come_riding_fast_poem_glosses_textual.php#BATTLEMENTSALL" /></l>
                    <l>And that its form thou now couldst trace</l>
                    <l>Froze to an icy wilderness.<ref type="gloss_textual" target="the_foam_globes_round_come_riding_fast_poem_glosses_textual.php#ANICYWILDERNESS" /></l>
                    <l>And that its portal vast &#x0026; old</l>
                    <l>All arched by the crisp ice cold.</l>
                    <l>And through whose chasms of paly green</l>
                    <l>The shivery sunshine shot between</l>
                    <l>Or trembling with a meteor light</l>
                    <l>Or dancing in the billows bright</l>
                    <l>Smiling aetherially through</l>
                    <l>The ghostlights of the crystal blue.</l>
                    
                    
                </lg>
